      "content": "but that's the thing... there isn't a \"small thing.\" any small thing i do just leads to another thing. it's like a loop that never ends. i look at my schedule and i just see a mountain i can't climb. i don't think things are gonna get better. i think i'm just supposed to fail. i just want the noise to stop. i want everything to just be quiet.",
